of <HI>Mechani&s;m,</HI> and &s;ome other <HI>Appearan|ces</HI>
of <HI>Nature</HI> that can no other ways be ac|counted
for, <HI>A. P.</HI> might infer that the
<PB N="33" REF="46">
Origin of the <HI>Faetus</HI> proceeded rather from
