the <HI>Exi&s;tenoe</HI> of a <HI>Deity</HI> from the <HI>Immecha|nical</HI>
Production of <HI>Animals:</HI> For let that
be how it will, Yet this is true and nece&s;&s;ar|ly
follows from his Rea&s;oning. Ay, but &s;ays
<HI>C. O.</HI> very learn'dly, the Seeds of <HI>Plants</HI> are
