ova lu&s;trando cicatriculam intueri,
quae utplurimum minima erat, &amp; licet vari|am
&s;ortiretur circum&s;criptionem, frequentius
tamen delineatam A.</HI> (where he has a con|fus'd
Scheme, which one can make nothing
<PB N="40" REF="53">
of) <HI>prae &s;e ferebat figuram, non longe d$ ce$|tro
globo&s;um condidumque corpus, qua&s;e mote
locabatur quod laceratum nullum pecudiare
