This looks a little &s;u&s;piciou&s;ly, as if Nature
did not bring about its Effects after the mo&s;t
<PB N="42" REF="55">
plain and &s;imple Manner: If there have been
<HI>Animalculs</HI> di&s;cover'd (as mo&s;t certainly
